reviews.title: Chinese standard food, friendly staff
reviews.text:
Nice, attentive service.
Standard food. Nicely decorated.
We had a rice table for 2 people.
Value for money in order.
There was a lot ordered and picked up.

reviews.title: Good Chinese Restaurant
reviews.text: This restaurant is located in the shopping area. There was not many choices for a vegetarian but they made it for us. The food was oke, friendly staff, good and quick service.

reviews.title: Service needs a big boost to make it worth while
reviews.text: Lovely interior, great food but ...... service sorely lacking. Staff sits and eat in front of you while ignoring you. Also -  no mention on their windows , menu or by the staff wrt the cards they accept or NOT accept for payment - which was highly embarrassing. Clearly - not all visitors are from Europe to have a Maestro card?

reviews.title: bad quality/price
reviews.text:
I had with my son a rice dish with meat, some additional rice, a small glass of coke and beer, and a small bottle of water for € 42.70. The bottle of SPA water was € 7.50
Not strange that there were only two families in the restaurant!

reviews.title: Good service and good food
reviews.text: I have enjoyed many dinners here and some take-aways. Both are always served with a smile and fresh and tasty. The restaurant is comfortable and offers a very large selection for every bodies taste. Very friendly family run restaurant. I will be back!

reviews.title: Delicious food and staff were nice, too.
reviews.text: We showed up at around 9:30pm looking to eat dinner. Most restaurants in town close around 10 and won't seat you after 9. We got lucky and were not disappointed by the quality of the food.

reviews.title: A Good Choice
reviews.text: If you like like chinese, this is one of the better choices around.
